# TypeScript and debug

## Before commit
- Run `pnpm type-check`. Fix any type errors before pushing.

## Error handling
- Do not use empty `catch` blocks. Log and/or rethrow:
```typescript
// BAD
try { await fetchData(); } catch (e) {}

// GOOD
try {
  await fetchData();
} catch (e) {
  console.error('Fetch failed', e);
  throw e;
}
```
- Keep user-facing error messages in Japanese; do not change them to English.
